I still gotta figure out all the details, but it seems like meatballs have a role in the power struggle in Terra. This sounds crazy, but the sentient meatballs are an actual thing, and they have a goal.

Following their traces, I stumbled into a monument that seems to be tied to the struggle against the meatballs' leader. 'The arbiter must stop him', but who is the arbiter, and when was this message sent?
